  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      During this proposed clinical trial, the investigators intend to evaluate the pharmacodynamic
      anti-inflammatory properties and safety of TPI ASM8, by investigating the effect on sputum
      eosinophils and the airway responses during an allergen challenge at different dose levels.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The early and late asthmatic response were both significantly attenuated by the highest dose
      of ASM8. The methacholine challenge and other parameters (ECP, mRNA knockdown on CCR3 and
      B-Chain of IL-3-Il-5 and GMCSF were attenuated by ASM8.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
